                            	  5003: _L_z07_UpdateArrowOrBoomerang_CompareLimit:
                            	  5004:     ; For boomerangs, compare it to the movement limit.
                            	  5005:     ; If it reached the limit, set state $20 and a new movement
                            	  5006:     ; limit of $10, and go handle the rest as if blocked.
                            	  5007:     ; State $20 will become $30 below in HandleArrowOrBoomerangBlocked.
                            	  5008:     ;
                            	  5009:     ; Otherwise, only animate and check collision as usual.
                            	  5010:     ;
                            	  5011:     ; In major state $30, ObjMovingLimit is a timer to change the state to $40.
                            	  5012:     ;
